https://dev.mysql.com/doc/mysql-apt-repo-quick-guide/en/#repo-qp-apt-install-from-source

＊＊＊第一次安装＊＊＊
１．添加mysql apt仓库配置
    １．１）下载配置deb包
        https://dev.mysql.com/get/mysql-apt-config_0.8.13-1_all.deb

    １．２）执行并配置
        sudo dpkg -i mysql-apt-config_0.8.13-1_all.deb

        １．２．１）Mysql Server & Cluster
        １．２．２）选择版本
        １．２．３）选择OK

    １．３）更新
        sudo apt-get update

    １．４）安装
        sudo apt-get install mysql-server

        配置root用户密码

    １．５）服务操作
        查看服务状态：sudo service mysql status
        停用服务：sudo service mysql stop
        启用服务：sudo service mysql start

    问题：
        １．重新配置后update报错（http://thedaneshproject.com/posts/n-skipping-acquire-of-configured-file-contrib-binary-i386-packages-as-repository-https-download-virtualbox-org-virtualbox-debian-bionic-inrelease-doesnt-support-architecture-i386/）
            eddychen2@eddychen2-VirtualBox:~$ sudo apt-get update
            命中:1 http://packages.treasuredata.com/3/ubuntu/xenial xenial InRelease
            命中:2 http://repo.mysql.com/apt/ubuntu xenial InRelease                                                                                                
            命中:3 https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu xenial InRelease       
            命中:4 http://cn.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu xenial InRelease                                                         
            命中:5 http://security.ubuntu.com/ubuntu xenial-security InRelease                                                 
            命中:6 http://cn.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu xenial-updates InRelease                                                
            命中:7 http://cn.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu xenial-backports InRelease 
            获取:8 http://repo.mysql.com/apt/ubuntu xenial/mysql-5.7 Sources [942 B]
            获取:9 http://repo.mysql.com/apt/ubuntu xenial/mysql-5.7 amd64 Packages [5,662 B]
            获取:10 http://repo.mysql.com/apt/ubuntu xenial/mysql-5.7 i386 Packages [5,674 B]
            已下载 12.3 kB，耗时 3秒 (3,179 B/s) 
            正在读取软件包列表... 完成
            N: 鉴于仓库 'http://packages.treasuredata.com/3/ubuntu/xenial xenial InRelease' 不支持 'i386' 体系结构，跳过配置文件 'contrib/binary-i386/Packages' 的捕获。

        解决方法：
            Change：deb https://download.virtualbox.org/virtualbox/debian bionic contrib
            To：deb [arch=amd64] https://download.virtualbox.org/virtualbox/debian bionic contrib
        重新update

２．升级（＊＊只能一步步升级，不能跨越升级＊＊）
    ２．１）重新配置
        sudo dpkg-reconfigure mysql-apt-config

    ２．２）更新apt 仓库
        sudo apt-get update

    ２．３）升级
        sudo apt-get install mysql-server

３．卸载
    ３．１） sudo apt-get remove mysql-server

    ３．２）remove any other software that was installed automatically with the MySQL server
        sudo apt-get autoremove